; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the saw_cost = true; break; path in finalize() when a posting
; has an explicit cost using @ syntax.  When the balance has exactly two
; commodities and one posting already has a cost, the code sets saw_cost
; and skips automatic per-unit cost calculation.

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash         $-1500.00

test reg
24-Jan-01 Buy Stock             Assets:Brokerage            10 AAPL      10 AAPL
                                Assets:Cash               $-1500.00    $-1500.00
                                                                         10 AAPL
end test
